COLUMNS

| Feature   | What it represents       |
| --------- | ------------------------ |
| month/day | When contact happened    |
| duration  | How long the call went   |
| campaign  | How many times contacted |
| pdays     | Recency of past contact  |
| previous  | Experience/history       |
| poutcome  | Past success/failure     |


campaign: Number of times this customer was contacted during this campaign

pdays: Number of days since the customer was last contacted in a previous campaign
        '-1' means customer was never contacted before

previous: Number of contacts performed before this campaign

poutcome: Outcome of the previous marketing campaign


